sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Browser (EventSource)
    participant API as API Server (Hono + Bun)
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant LiteLLM as LiteLLM (Model Gateway)
    participant Redis as Redis (Pub/Sub)
    participant Client2 as Other Clients (same conversation)

    Note over Client, Client2: SSE Token Streaming Flow

    Client->>API: POST /conversations/{id}/messages { content: "..." }

    API->>DB: INSERT message (role: user, status: created)
    DB-->>API: messageId

    API->>DB: INSERT message (role: assistant, status: streaming)
    DB-->>API: assistantMessageId

    API-->>Client: 200 OK SSE stream opens (Content-Type: text/event-stream)

    API->>LiteLLM: POST /chat/completions (stream: true)

    loop Token-by-token streaming
        LiteLLM-->>API: data: {"choices":[{"delta":{"content":"token"}}]}

        API->>Redis: PUBLISH conv:{id} { type: "token", data: "token" }

        API-->>Client: event: token, data: {"content":"token","messageId":"..."}

        Redis-->>Client2: SSE push via other API pod (fan-out)
    end

    LiteLLM-->>API: data: [DONE]

    API->>DB: UPDATE message SET content=full_text, status=completed, token_count=N, finished_at=NOW()

    API->>Redis: PUBLISH conv:{id} { type: "stream.done", messageId: "..." }

    API-->>Client: event: stream.done, data: {"messageId":"...","tokenCount":N}

    Note over Client, Client2: Heartbeat (keeps SSE alive, idleTimeout=0)

    loop Every 15 seconds while SSE open
        API-->>Client: : heartbeat (SSE comment)
    end

    Note over Client, Client2: Error Recovery

    alt LiteLLM error mid-stream
        LiteLLM-->>API: HTTP 500 or connection drop
        API->>DB: UPDATE message SET status=failed, error="..."
        API->>Redis: PUBLISH conv:{id} { type: "stream.error" }
        API-->>Client: event: stream.error, data: {"error":"Model unavailable"}
    end

    alt Client reconnects (EventSource auto-retry)
        Client->>API: GET /conversations/{id}/events (Last-Event-ID: 42)
        API->>DB: SELECT tokens WHERE message_id AND seq > 42
        DB-->>API: Missed tokens
        API-->>Client: Replay missed events + resume stream
    end
